// SET15 SetMaxPumpDuty decimal value translate to hexadecimal in service menu 64 to 254
// First find out the upper and lower limit of the waterpump. Trial and arror by injecting a number as payload to the mqtt topic. fill them in in the two lines below!!!
//
var lowerlimit=80; // Lowest value giving a change in resulting in flow = 80 >> corresponds to 12 L/min.
var upperlimit=149; // Hihghes value giving a change in resulting flow = 149 >> corresonds to 20 L/min.
//
var range=(upperlimit-lowerlimit); // This is the range of operation for the waterpump. You need to test this manually and correct the values if needed.


msg.payload = ((msg.payload) / 100 * range) + lowerlimit; // calculation
msg.payload = Number(msg.payload).toFixed(0);
msg.payload = parseFloat(msg.payload);

return msg;

